results.title: [Atresia of the aortic arch. A rare cause of asymmetrical arterial hypertension in adulthood].
results.text_hl: Cautious antihypertensive drug treatment with @<m>CHEMICAL_Atenolol</m> @CHEMICAL_MESH:D001262 @@@Atenolol@@@ (25 mg daily) reduced the pressure in the right arm to 180/90 mmHg.
